The paper deals with computer vision techniques for extracting interpersonal eye gaze from video recordings, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper focuses on affective communication and human-computer interaction, which are subfields of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for clustering and prediction, which are subfields of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the analysis of communication behavior, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper mentions the use of video recordings, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
